            <p><span style="color:#ffa937;">&#10004;</span> Track product pages</p>
            <p><span style="color:#ffa937;">&#10004;</span> Track checkout conversions</p>
			<p><span style="color:#ffa937;">&#10004;</span> Track customer conversions</p>
			<p><span style="color:#ffa937;">&#10004;</span> Upgrade plan: £4 per extra site</p>


           <br />
            
        </div>
        
    </div>
</div>


<div class="row radius" style="background-color:white;padding-left:4%;padding-right:2%;padding-top:2%;padding-bottom:2%;margin-top:4%;font-size:13pt;">
            <div class="col-md-2">
                <img style="max-width: 80%";text-align: center;vertical-align: middle;" src="~/Content/paypal-logo.png" />
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-10">
                <label class="charcoal smalltext alignleft"><span class="mediumtext yellowfont">We adhere to PayPal's strict rules and requirements</span><br>
				After you signup you will be able to login. When you login on the first occasion you will be asked to register your subscription through PayPal. We don't store any card details and no payment will taken unless you continue beyond your 14-day free trial. You can cancel on your dashboard at anytime.</label><br />
                <p></p>
            </div>
        </div>
<script>
    function check(input) {
        if (input.value != document.getElementById('password').value) {
            input.setCustomValidity('Confirm password Must be Matching to password.');
        } else {
            // input is valid -- reset the error message
            input.setCustomValidity('');
        }
    }
</script>